      "writtenOn": "2019-08-03T00:03:07Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "i am not sure how this is supposed to be used. Specifically, we need to \n\n- read invocation\n- see if it finalized, exit if it is\n- write result rows\n\nall in one transaction. This is not possible with this abstraction. I think we are over-generalizing",
      "revId": "f7901f5816ba144b2eb15c4c7a6cfbb48d1eb6d1",
      "serverId": "3ce6091f-6c88-37e8-8c75-72f92ae8dfba",
